title: Japan: Mikki rules at Kyoto with second Grade 1 in Shuka
text: Japan: Mikki rules at Kyoto with second Grade 1 in Shuka Sunday, 18 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) JAPANESE OAKS winner, and 2-1 favourite, Mikki Queen (Yasutoshi Ikee/Suguru Hamanaka) overcame crowding on the final bend to surge clear and take her Grade 1 tally to two in the final leg of the fillies' triple crown.
